**70 AD = STRONGEST FIT for vv15-22** (trigger→flight→tribulation→shortening). **ABSENT for vv23-27** (supernatural deception, visible parousia). This confirms the DUAL-HORIZON structure the whole discourse exhibits: a near-historical fulfillment pattern that points to an eschatological consummation.

**ROADMAP:** (1) RAPTURE/GATHERING — absent from vv15-28; elect are IN the tribulation (v22,24). Gathering appears v31, POST-tribulation. (2) RETURN OF CHRIST — v27 defines parousia: lightning, universal, unmistakable. Destroys the lawless one (2Th 2:8). (3) FALL OF BABYLON — "flee" = Jer 51:6/Rev 18:4; ptoma-gathering = fallen Babylon; the carcase = the fallen system. (4) SUDDEN DESTRUCTION — tribulation is the covenant-judgment falling; shortened for mercy. (5) DAYS OF NOAH — Luke 17:26-37 frames identical material in Days-of-Noah context; Lot's wife = backward-looking attachment to the condemned world. (6) THIRD DAY — "saved out of it" (Jer 30:7) = Hos 6:2 pattern of deliverance through, not from. (7) DAY AS 1000 YEARS — "those days shortened" = God's sovereign control of duration.

**MISSING/ABSENT:** TRUMPET — v31. GATHERING — v31. DARKNESS — v29. SLEEP — this is the maximally-awake panel; urgency peaks. NAME — absent here; the persecutors/false Christs claim Christ's name but the true NAME (covenant authority) is revealed only at the lightning-parousia.
